metadata.name: AIDA
metadata.description:
Aida is the goddess or personified spirit of force, power, might, bodily strength and compulsion. She, is the winged enforcer of The Universe who stood in attendance by the absolute divine throne. Aida is one of the most powerful deities in the D1v1ne pantheon. 

6200 x 6200 px 600 DPI  
Ani Mkhitaryan, 2022  
www.an1.io
